<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>전시회 목록 - SKKU Faculty Art Gallery</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <h1>SKKU Faculty Art Gallery</h1>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">홈</a></li>
                <li><a href="/exhibition">전시회</a></li>
                <li><a href="/notice">공지사항</a></li>
                <li><a href="/user/login">로그인</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="archive-header">
            <h2>작품 아카이브</h2>
            <p>성균관대학교 미술 동아리의 작품들을 한눈에 볼 수 있는 공간입니다.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="exhibition-categories">
            <h3>카테고리</h3>
            <div class="category-list">
                <a href="/exhibition/category/painting" class="category-item">회화</a>
                <a href="/exhibition/category/drawing" class="category-item">드로잉</a>
                <a href="/exhibition/category/digital" class="category-item">디지털 아트</a>
                <a href="/exhibition/category/sculpture" class="category-item">조소</a>
                <a href="/exhibition/category/mixed" class="category-item">혼합 매체</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="exhibition-list">
            <h3>최근 작품</h3>
            <div class="exhibition-grid">
                <article class="exhibition-card">
                    <a href="/exhibition/1">
                        <img src="/images/artworks/painting1.jpg" alt="수채화 작품">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h4>봄의 풍경</h4>
                            <p class="artist">김예술</p>
                            <p class="category">회화</p>
                            <p class="date">2024.02</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </article>
                <article class="exhibition-card">
                    <a href="/exhibition/2">
                        <img src="/images/artworks/digital1.jpg" alt="디지털 아트">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h4>도시의 밤</h4>
                            <p class="artist">이디지털</p>
                            <p class="category">디지털 아트</p>
                            <p class="date">2024.01</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </article>
                <article class="exhibition-card">
                    <a href="/exhibition/3">
                        <img src="/images/artworks/drawing1.jpg" alt="연필 드로잉">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h4>자화상</h4>
                            <p class="artist">박드로잉</p>
                            <p class="category">드로잉</p>
                            <p class="date">2024.01</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 SKKU Faculty Art Gallery. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html> 